description:
Shoot, attack, and stave off the assault by defeating all the Invaders on the screen. After annihilating a battalion of Invaders and defeating the Boss, players move on to the next stage. But beware of different types of Invaders, each with their own unique abilities -- it's &quot;Game Over&quot; if players lose all of their stock cannons!

Emulated with PPSSPP which is Xbox360 controller compatible.

Read the README!! text file for more info.


Recommended System Requirements:

Core 2 duo 2.4GHz or higher.

nVidia GeForce GT 610 / ATI Radeon HD 5 series or higher.

2 Gig of ram or more.

Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8 32 or 64bit OS


